flex-basis: width

this property is used like max-width , in this we have given max width to an element if below the 200px it will automaticlly small down.


flex-grow: how much times you wanted to grow this item;

flex-grow is a type of min-width and will grow relative to other items


flex-shirnk:  how much times you wanted to shirnk this item compared to other items




